# Diátaxis marker

The presence of this file signals that `wiki/` follows the Diátaxis four-mode
convention (tutorials / how-to / reference / explanation) and may be subject
to `check-wiki.py --strict` linting.

Architectural decisions live in the living designs under `wiki/designs/` — each
design's amendment log records the decisions it embodies. (The standalone ADR
model is retired.)
